luister, en julle sal lewe.</text>
<ref>Jesaja 55:3</ref>
</parol>
</theword>
<theword date='2017-09-30'>
<title>Die Woord vir Saterdag 30 September 2017</title>
<parol book='43' chapter='14' verse='10' id='J14v10'>
